parseJodaJdk

public static ValidationUtil.ParsedDate parseJodaJdk(String pattern,
                                                     String value)
Parses the pattern into a date object using Joda date and time API. The returned date data will be stored in JDK date objects.

Parameters:
pattern - The date/time pattern to use when parsing.
value - The value that should match the given pattern.
Returns:
The ValidationUtil.ParsedDate object when parsing was successful, or null.

parseJoda

public static JodaDateUtil.ParsedDate parseJoda(String pattern,
                                                String value)
Parses the pattern into a date object using Joda date and time API. The returned date data will also be stored in Joda API objects.

Parameters:
pattern - The date/time pattern to use when parsing.
value - The value that should match the given pattern.
Returns:
The JodaDateUtil.ParsedDate object when parsing was successful, or null.
